Package exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidDominoesCSVFile
    The csv file provided as Domino source is invalid.
    InvalidDominoPosition
    The Player is trying to add a Domino at an invalid Position.
    MaxCrownsLandPortionExceeded
    A LandPortion has exceeded the max number authorized of crowns.
    NoMoreDominoInGameStack
    There is no more Domino in the Game stack.
    NotEnoughDominoesInGameStack
    There not enough Dominos in the Game stack.
    PlayerColorAlreadyUsed
    A Player is already using the PlayerColor desired.
